Class FoodRules

  • java.lang.Object
    • FoodRules

  • public class FoodRules
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will handle the food rules used by our cookbook. This class will delineate what warrants a meat, seafood, etc. It will also help in labeling food restrictions such as vegetarian and vegan.
    Author:
    Craig Lombardo

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      FoodRules()
      This constructor method takes no parameters and sets all of the items included in each category, as specified in the class description.
